          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Reinforcing American-Made Products Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Violent Crime Control and Law Enforcement Act of 1994 to specify that&nbsp;the Federal Trade Commission's regulation of the labeling of products as "Made in the U.S.A." or "Made in America"&nbsp;supersedes any conflicting state laws. </p>]]></text>
